IRANA|work=Directory of Members|publisher=[[Parliament of Sri Lanka]]|date=|accessdate=14 March 2013}}{{Dead link|date=January 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slelections.gov.lk/pdf/GE2010_preferences/Galle_pref_GE2010.pdf|title=Parliamentary Elections \u22122010 |work=|publisher=Department of Elections, Sri Lanka|date=|accessdate=14 March 2013}}</ref>\n\n==Panabokke==\n*[[Tikiri Bandara Panabokke I]] \u2013 Member of the Legislative Council of Ceylon\n**Sir [[Tikiri Bandara Panabokke II]] \u2013  Minister of Health in the State Council of Ceylon<ref>http://www.rootsweb.ancestry.com/~lkawgw/gen3116.html</ref><ref>{{Google books |id=eUF_rS8FEoIC |page=815 |title=Twentieth Century Impressions of Ceylon }}</ref> \n***[[Theodore Braybrooke Panabokke]] \u2013 Deputy Minister of Justice and Agriculture\n\n==Perera==\n* Festus Perera,<!--  Reference:   http://www.dailynews.lk/epaper/art.asp?id=2013/01/14/pg03_10&pt=p&h=    --> Government Minister, Member of Parliament + [[Larine Perera]] Member of Parliament, Provincial Minister, Provincial Councillor\n** [[Niroshan Perera]], Member of Parliament and State Minister of Youth Affairs<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.lk/directory_of_members/ViewMember.do?memID=3152|title=NIROSHAN PERERA|work=Directory of Members|publisher=[[Parliament of Sri Lanka]]|date=|accessdate=14 March 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101013024815/http://www.parliament.lk/directory_of_members/ViewMember.do?memID=3152|archive-date=13 October 2010|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slelections.gov.lk/pdf/GE2010_preferences/Puttalama_pref_GE2010.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100513041821/http://www.slelections.gov.lk/pdf/GE2010_preferences/Puttalama_pref_GE2010.pdf|url-status=dead|archive-date=13 May 2010|title=Parliamentary Elections \u22122010|publisher=Department of Elections, Sri Lanka|accessdate=14 March 2013}}</ref>\n\n==Premachandra==\n*[[