ika |work=dailymirror.lk |date=31 March 2014}}</ref>\n\n==Ponnambalam==\n* [[G. G. Ponnambalam]] KC (1901\u20131977), founder and leader of the [[All Ceylon Tamil Congress]], Government Minister, Member of Parliament, Member of State Council\n** [[Kumar Ponnambalam]] (1940\u20132000), leader of the [[All Ceylon Tamil Congress]],<ref>{{cite book|last=Rajasingham|first=K. T.|title=Sri Lanka: The Untold Story|url=http://www.atimes.com/ind-pak/CJ13Df01.html|chapter=Chapter 10: Lord Soulbury and his soulless report}}</ref> presidential candidate (1982)\n*** [[Gajendrakumar Ponnambalam]] (1974\u2013 ), leader of the [[All Ceylon Tamil Congress]],<ref>{{cite news|title=Kumar Ponnambalam memorial held in Vavuniya|url=http://www.tamilguardian.com/article.asp?articleid=9686|work=[[Tamil Guardian]]|date=9 January 2014}}</ref> Member of Parliament<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slelections.gov.lk/pdf/preference2001GE.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304015155/http://www.slelections.gov.lk/pdf/preference2001GE.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-date=2010-03-04 |title=General Election 2001 Preferences |publisher=Department of Elections, Sri Lanka }}</ref>\n\n==Premadasa==\n* [[Ranasinghe Premadasa]] (1924\u20131993), [[President of Sri Lanka]], [[Prime Minister of Sri Lanka]], Government Minister, Member of Parliament<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.island.lk/index.php?page_cat=article-details&page=article-details&code_title=77978|title=The Island|website=www.island.lk}}</ref> + Hema Wickrematunge\n**[[Sajith Premadasa]] (1967 \u2013 ), [[Leader of the Opposition]], Government Minister, Member of Parliament<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsfirst.lk/2015/08/18/general-election-2015-hambantota-district-preferential-votes-announced/|title=General Election 2015 : Hambantota district preferential votes announced|last=|first=|date=|website=|access-date=}}</ref><ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=https://elections.gov.lk/web/en/elections/elections-results/parliamentary-elections-